Class ExtensibleObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.telekom.m2m.cot.restsdk.util.ExtensibleObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Alarm, AuditRecord, BulkOperation, CurrentUser, Event, Group, GroupReference, ManagedObject, Measurement, NewDeviceRequest, Operation, Progress, RetentionRule, Role, RoleReference, SmartRequest, SmartResponse, User, UserReference

    public class ExtensibleObject
extends Object
    Extensible object is a base class of all domain objects. It handles the (de-)serialization parts.

    Created by Patrick Steinert on 31.01.16.
